iv class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-beded03\" data-id=\"beded03\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c3de95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6c3de95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><b>Amalie Hylland<\/b><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-a555700 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"a555700\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a8a0b73\" data-id=\"a8a0b73\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1e2e47 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1e2e47\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong><br><\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Amalie er utdannet og autorisert psykolog i Spania, og tilbyr online terapi til norske klienter. Hun har en omfattende erfaring som klinisk psykolog.&nbsp;Hun har arbeidet med et bredt utvalg av psykiske helseutfordringer som angst, fobier, grubling, depresjon, sosiale vansker og ferdigheter, grensesetting, selvhevdelse, utbrenthet, selvtillit, selvbilde, prokrastinering, selvskading, diverse tvangslidelser, og psykose.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong><br><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-246ec35 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"246ec35\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-edd11ce\" data-id=\"edd11ce\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-7aa53e4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7aa53e4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-extended\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-ffb5e66\" data-id=\"ffb5e66\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b1e4bf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9b1e4bf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Det betyr at hun har en s\u00e6rskilt kompetanse n\u00e5r det gjelder \u00e5 kartlegge og forst\u00e5 atferdsm\u00f8nstre, hvordan de kan p\u00e5virke livskvaliteten v\u00e5r p\u00e5 en negativ m\u00e5te, og hvordan endre atferd og situasjoner som for\u00e5rsaker problemer.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21544f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"21544f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Amalie har yrkeserfaring fra en internasjonal klinikk i Madrid, og har ogs\u00e5 arbeidet som psykolog for studenter ved IE University.&nbsp;For tiden kombinerer hun sitt kliniske arbeid med \u00e5 v\u00e6re foreleser ved det psykologiske fakultet p\u00e5 European University of Madrid.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><br><\/p>\n<p>I tillegg til studiet i klinisk psykologi, har Amalie fullf\u00f8rt en mastergrad i atferdsmodifikasjon fra The Therapeutic Institute of Madrid (ITEMA).&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Gjennom dette studiet har hun utdypet sin forst\u00e5else for hvorfor vi gj\u00f8r det vi gj\u00f8r, og hva vi kan gj\u00f8re n\u00e5r v\u00e5r atferd og omstendigheter for\u00e5rsaker problemer.&nbsp;<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-c9a1a0e\" data-id=\"c9a1a0e\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dcc5971 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"dcc5971\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t